metadata.name: Hope Street #1/11
metadata.description:
"Tony's Historical Parakeet Restaurant Bar & Lounge. 1966 Hope St. Chocolate City LA, 70119. We survived Katrina, Rita, Gustav, and Ike. We're Back."

Looking at the Parakeet from across the street, this iconic building represents all that is sacred in New Orleans - culture, community, history. Golden hour, fittingly at the intersection of Orleans and Hope Street.
